metadata.name: Bird
metadata.description:
ChatGPT: "I used geometric elements and drawing primitives to create a complex, recognizable bird shape without external resources or random generation. The bird's body parts are drawn with relative sizing and positioning, allowing easy scaling. The GaussianBlur filter adds depth and visual complexity, simulating light diffusion and producing smooth color transitions for a more natural appearance."

RARJPEG on a ZIP file.
